        {
            "title": "早期民調顯示高市早苗選情向好 有望在眾議院拿下更多席位",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 追蹤投票趨勢的早期民調顯示，日本首相高市早苗領導的執政黨<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:自民黨;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/自民黨\">自民黨</a>有望在眾議院選舉中贏得更多席位，甚至有可能單獨拿下多數席位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上任僅三個月，高市早苗便將自己的首相之位押在了全國大選上，呼籲選民支持其積極財政政策、暫時降低消費稅、在防務和外國人問題上採取更強硬立場。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">她已放話，如果自民黨及其執政夥伴維新會不能贏得多數席位，她將立即辭職。上周五眾議院解散前，執政聯盟擁有233個席位，剛剛過半數線。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-0fb0729d-5af2-39ef-9156-b3b44129257f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"高市早苗1月27日在東京為選舉造勢。攝影師：Toru Hanai/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/qCNyhDwPWiXT15GnRwmiYA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/90bbe3962722e49489d1da889a8ed114\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">高市早苗1月27日在東京為選舉造勢。攝影師：Toru Hanai/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日經新聞和讀賣新聞的民調顯示，自民黨此次可能單獨贏得超過233席。共同社則估計，自民黨和維新會聯合起來可能拿下多數席位。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">所有民調都顯示，由原最大在野黨立憲民主黨和自民黨前執政聯盟夥伴公明黨合併組建的新政黨「中道改革聯合」，恐難實現議席數量成長。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些民調著眼於特定選區的投票意向，與之前主要聚焦全國投票偏好的調查相比，能更清晰地預示選情走向。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Early Polls Show Japan’s Takaichi on Track to Expand Majority</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A9%E6%9C%9F%E6%B0%91%E8%AA%BF%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E9%AB%98%E5%B8%82%E6%97%A9%E8%8B%97%E9%81%B8%E6%83%85%E5%90%91%E5%A5%BD-%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E5%9C%A8%E7%9C%BE%E8%AD%B0%E9%99%A2%E6%8B%BF%E4%B8%8B%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E5%B8%AD%E4%BD%8D-021709209.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-29 15:58:46",
