        {
            "title": "中資地產股陸港兩地勁升 房企「三條紅線」指標淡出報導提振情緒",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 曾經壓制中國房地產行業的「三條紅線」指標據報淡出，顯示政策對行業復甦和房企的進一步支持，中資地產股周四受提振在陸港兩地走高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博行業研究(BI)中資地產指數盤中最大漲近11%，創下去年7月10日以來盤中最大漲幅，融創中國最大勁升逾30%領漲。A股中上證房地產指數也在五大行業分類中表現最佳。此前本地媒體新京報報導稱，房企「三條紅線」指標淡出，多家房企稱不再需要每月上報。不過據彭博引述知情人士的報導，早在2023年中國開發商就停止定期報告「三條紅線」的情況。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-99c85b1f-deee-3129-9e72-a01ad56eb88b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國監管層自2020年推出「三條紅線」管控房企債務規模以來，中國恆大等高槓桿房企再融資開始面臨挑戰，疊加疫情衝擊、經濟成長放緩，銷售逐步陷入低迷，房地產業自此陷入了漫長調整，大多數房企均已在公開市場違約並努力進行債務重組，最新萬科的數只境內債延期兌付計畫獲得了持有人通過。當前政策已轉向支持和穩定地產市場，整體行業能否止跌回穩，仍需進一步觀察銷售等更多指標。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">東亞銀行策略師Bosco Wu在採訪中表示，鑒於多數開發商已無力承擔額外債務並縮減業務規模，三條紅線已不再適用當前的房地產市場，「這可能預示著房地產行業限制將進一步放寬，但銷售的進一步改善仍需買家信心恢復和更多有效的刺激政策。」</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/wuueAhSjti8owi0aT_1mXQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/0698518be39f497b42fa73a861dc3e45\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報導稱「三條紅線」政策自2020年8月試點，2021年全面推行，包括剔除預收款後的資產負債率不得超過70%、淨負債率不得超過100%，以及現金短債比不得小於1倍。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上海易居房地產研究院副院長嚴躍進在採訪中表示，目前地產行業整體負債規模膨脹勢頭得到根本遏制，「當前市場的主要矛盾從防止行業過熱，轉變為‘防風險、保交付、促穩定’等工作。」他認為，2026年將更強調對支持住房消費、開發貸、保交房、存量債務化解、城中村改造等工作的推進，相關融資工作將有進一步支持的可能。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國知名私募基金公司半夏投資的創始人李蓓近期加入看多地產的行列。其在微信公眾號上表示中國地產的大拐點確認，稱二手房的成交加速上升，掛牌持續下降，供減需增是拐點的明確信號，同時二手房價格上跌幅收窄，在價格上也看到明確信號。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">具有國資背景的萬科的債務問題是中國地產行業新的聚焦點。其在最新的公告中稱深鐵集團向其提供不超過23.6億元借款，兩只中票持有人據悉已收到首批兌付款，亦緩解了市場情緒。萬科在港股邁向連續兩日上漲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">(新增第二段知情人士報導、第六段評論)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E8%B3%87%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E8%82%A1%E9%99%B8%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%A9%E5%9C%B0%E5%8B%81%E5%8D%87-%E6%88%BF%E4%BC%81-%E4%B8%89%E6%A2%9D%E7%B4%85%E7%B7%9A-%E6%8C%87%E6%A8%99%E6%B7%A1%E5%87%BA%E5%A0%B1%E5%B0%8E%E6%8F%90%E6%8C%AF%E6%83%85%E7%B7%92-034559072.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-29 14:47:28",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中國房企據悉早已開始停止上報「三條紅線」指標",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 據知情人士透露，早在2023年，相關部門放寬所謂的「三條紅線」要求後，就已有中國開發商開始停止定期上報相關指標了。這些債務指標推動了該國前所未有的樓市下滑。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上述人士說，至少有三家開發商在2023年前後停止向監管機構提交相關數據，另有一些開發商則從去年年初開始暫停上報。由於事未公開，知情人士要求匿名。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國地產股周四上漲，之前《新京報》報導了「三條紅線」淡出一事。此舉表明中國當局對房地產的立場顯著轉變；這個行業曾經是經濟成長的主要引擎，如今卻成了長期負累。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-1d45a95d-a050-3ef8-b54e-2818a7da19b9-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中指控股分析師Liu Shui表示：「‘三道紅線’政策目標已經實現。激進的民營多數發生債務違約，房地產風險逐步釋放及出清，‘三道紅線’繼續實施已經無實際意義。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：中國「三道紅線」政策對房地產公司的意義：QuickTake</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China Developers Ceased Reporting ‘Three Red Lines’ for Years</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Zheng Li.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%88%BF%E4%BC%81%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E6%97%A9%E5%B7%B2%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E4%B8%8A%E5%A0%B1-%E4%B8%89%E6%A2%9D%E7%B4%85%E7%B7%9A-%E6%8C%87%E6%A8%99-051529444.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-29 14:47:31",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "彭博新聞午間分享 你會想知道的五件事",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Photographer: Carl Court/Getty Images\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"666\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/qqgY.fsCcKeH4COBpVLgMg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY2Ng--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/4b9a2b33c303bf51e680588061d8bd9f\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Photographer: Carl Court/Getty Images</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">按兵不動</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯儲會以10比2的投票結果維持利率不變，在連續三次降息後按下寬鬆暫停鍵。鮑威爾稱美國經濟前景明顯改善，就業市場出現企穩跡象。期貨市場預計6月之前不會有利率變動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">暴跌</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">印尼股市連續第二天暴跌並觸發熔斷，之前MSCI對當地股票可投資性發出警告，並可能將其降級為前沿市場。券商也紛紛調降印尼股市評級，高盛表示極端情境下可能引發超130億美元資金外流。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">AI未來</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">特斯拉計畫今年投入200億美元用於戰略轉型，精簡電動汽車產品線，將資源向機器人和AI領域傾斜。馬斯克還稱，特斯拉需要自建巨型晶片廠「TeraFab」，因現有供應商已無法滿足需求。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-8e79180e-9f80-3ea1-8592-5cd62e6b8fda-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">所剩無幾</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普再對伊朗發出軍事打擊威脅，稱留給後者的時間所剩無幾，要麼與美國達成核協議，要麼將面臨比去年6月更猛烈的打擊。伊朗對此表示，逼不得已時將以「前所未有的方式」回應美國。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">務實外交</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英國首相斯塔默開啟訪華之旅，釋放務實外交信號。他在與中國國家主席習近平會面時呼籲建立「更成熟」的雙邊關係。斯塔默表示中國在全球舞台上扮演著重要角色，儘管存在分歧，仍希望深化兩國關係。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Photographer: Carl Court/Getty Images\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"666\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Q2FA4LT9szEYULo.rWPc_Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY2Ng--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/9bea7694a4a1ec4a47e723cb3f66d4d3\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Photographer: Carl Court/Getty Images</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BD%AD%E5%8D%9A%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E5%8D%88%E9%96%93%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB-%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%83%E6%83%B3%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%94%E4%BB%B6%E4%BA%8B-043206506.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-29 13:11:18",
