            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中國地產股飆升 有報導稱「三條紅線」指標開始淡出",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國房地產股票飆升，之前有本地媒體報導稱，多家房企已無需每月上報「三道紅線」債務指標。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博行業研究(BI)中資地產股指數周四一度上漲8.1%，創7月以來最大單日漲幅。其中融創中國領漲，其港股一度飆升31%。碧桂園也一度上漲逾23%。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/TR.MYjNnBjcudzH1P6OGdg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/9a146f28868ac1f045908e47cbf56f47\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">《新京報》周三晚間報導稱，多家開發商不再需要每月上報「三條紅線」指標。這些債務指標於2021年正式推出，旨在遏制開發商的財務槓桿。如果此事屬實，那麼這一監管鬆綁措施將標志著當局為遏制樓市持續下滑而實施的一次重大政策放鬆之舉；樓市長期不景氣正在拖累該世界第二大經濟體。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d07482f6-5070-3c64-94c9-0de52730e4d4-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「三條紅線上報要求的取消，對市場情緒的影響大於實際影響，」東亞銀行策略師Bosco Wu表示。「其可能預示著房地產行業的限制政策將會進一步放鬆。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Chinese Property Stocks Jump on Report ‘Three Red Lines’ to Ease</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E8%82%A1%E9%A3%86%E5%8D%87-%E6%9C%89%E5%A0%B1%E5%B0%8E%E7%A8%B1-%E4%B8%89%E6%A2%9D%E7%B4%85%E7%B7%9A-%E6%8C%87%E6%A8%99%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B%E6%B7%A1%E5%87%BA-033113970.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-29 12:08:44",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "Information稱輝達等公司正在商談向OpenAI投資至多600億美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> Information引述知情人士的消息報導，輝達、微軟和亞馬遜正在商討向OpenAI投資至多600億美元，作為新一輪大規模融資的一部分。 </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報導稱，計畫中的投資將是總額最高1000億美元融資輪的一部分。現有投資者輝達正在洽談投資至多300億美元，另一位現有投資者微軟則計畫投資不到100億美元。報導指出，新投資者亞馬遜的投資額可能超過100億美元，甚至超過200億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報導稱，上述投資是軟銀計畫追加的300億美元之外的投資。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a4999c0d-3727-35a9-b4ab-cb6af0c8c1e8-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：軟銀據悉正在商談向OpenAI追加投資不超過300億美元</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Nvidia, Others in Talks for OpenAI Investment, Information Says</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/information%E7%A8%B1%E8%BC%9D%E9%81%94%E7%AD%89%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%AD%A3%E5%9C%A8%E5%95%86%E8%AB%87%E5%90%91openai%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%87%B3%E5%A4%9A600%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-032848789.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-29 12:08:46",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
